## Performance Optimizations

* ‚úÖ Cached diagnostic results using Streamlit session state
* ‚úÖ LLM queries do not re-trigger diagnostics
* ‚úÖ Efficient cluster switching handling
* ‚úÖ Controlled AI output length for clarity

